{"tid":2195272,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"特朗普提美中經濟脫鈎　王毅：有國家把數據安全政治化","createTime":"2020-09-09T05:21:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-09T23:13:02.000Z","uid":130626,"like":4,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"9c36e68dc1f8236807bf0f52b5636c5306a15e58","tid":2195272,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T05:21:46.000Z","msg":"美國總統特朗普再次提出中美經濟脫鈎的想法，說應該開始思考脫鈎的問題，將就業職位從中國轉移回美國，終止對中國的依賴。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普又批評，民主黨總統候選人拜登對華政策軟弱，說如果拜登當選，將是中國的勝利。<br />\n<br />\n美國近期以國家安全為理由，加強對中國企業的限制。國務委員兼外長王毅在北京出席全球數位治理研討會時，不點名指有國家把數據安全問題政治化，甚至不惜造謠抹黑，違背國際關係基本準則，亦嚴重干擾和阻礙全球合作與發展。王毅又說中國願意發起《全球數據安全倡議》，歡迎各方積極參與。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1548553-20200908.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1548553-20200908.htm&d=Yvf7L03l0%2FKFASkGPCPwgy3KoYHjImyLH66vjnFGY4M%3D&h=2278ac34\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1548553-20200908.htm&h=35f5f31e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1548553-20200908.htm</a>"},{"pid":"714d0c3b5e06c6990b5336d7aaabb080e35ff523","tid":2195272,"uid":13663,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T05:22:45.000Z","msg":"有國家=其他國家？"},{"pid":"7143e39ca85bee303f552b1c8899f0c3156d01b9","tid":2195272,"uid":155095,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"714d0c3b5e06c6990b5336d7aaabb080e35ff523","tid":2195272,"uid":13663,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T05:22:45.000Z","msg":"有國家=其他國家？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-09T05:23:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EL0Mg7gVAAIgNk0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEL0Mg7gVAAIgNk0.jpg&h=c670fe60&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fb9c615ecc420831d789f22fc2d6b282c8c74799","tid":2195272,"uid":81562,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTi